  "text": "The camera prototype was integrated into the demonstrator setup at the TopoTomo beam line [CITATION_1] and was successfully tested at ANKA with a moderate X-ray flux density. Several thousand of radiographies have been acquired at full speed (340 frames/s) in streaming mode; one X-ray radiography is shown in Fig. 14 . The FPN noise contribution has been drastically reduced by the procedure described earlier, and the dark noise has also been reduced to an appropriate SNR level. The spatial resolution has been measured to be a few micrometers.",
